description: Updates an Amazon QuickSight application with a token exchange grant. This operation only supports Amazon QuickSight applications that are registered with IAM Identity Center.

parameters.name: AwsAccountId
parameters.description: The ID of the Amazon Web Services account to be updated with a token exchange grant.

parameters.name: Namespace
parameters.description: The namespace of the Amazon QuickSight application.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The HTTP status of the request.

nested_items.name: RequestId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services request ID for this operation.
